<div data-pf-editor-version="legacy" class="sc-jeyqhx jfeuyL __pf __pf_a_SrDJC0"><div data-section-id="pf-90b4" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-134df04fd9b9-5_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-6_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-7_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-8_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-10_">TESTIMONIALS</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-11_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-12_"><div data-slider="{'slidesToShow':{'all':1,'laptop':1,'tablet':1,'mobile':1},'slidesToScroll':{'all':1,'laptop':1,'tablet':1,'mobile':1},'loop':false,'autoPlay':false,'autoPlayDelay':3000,'pauseOnHover':false,'maxHeight':false,'id':'e7a9b19f-8a95-47d9-8ce6-4144168f0b2c'}" class="sc-bcSJDS sc-jkTopv ezNXrm jzWddv pf-134df04fd9b9-13_ testimonial_slider glider-n-1 " style="visibility:hidden;height:620.4000244140625px;opacity:0" data-pf-type="Slider2"><div class="glider" style="--g-xs:0px"><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-377_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-376_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-375_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-371_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-370_">When I first started HER Year, I was moving to a new country, completely on my own, completely burnt out, and physically unhealthy from the stress of the past year. Throughout my time in HER Year, I learned to listen to my intuition more about relationships/friendships that were working or not working in my life. <strong>I got and stayed SOBER because, despite the fact that I've been trying to get sober for a decade, I never FELT the commitment to my future self deep in my core until this program.</strong><br><br>Every month, I would tune in to the HER Year modules and different things would speak to me. But knowing I had this community behind me, all trying to grow in our own ways,<strong> inspired me to continue to come back to myself when things got really hard.</strong><br><br>The December HER Year event was the most expansive aspect of this program. It pushed me out of my comfort zone in the safest way and allowed me to receive the wisdom from women who I thought would be very different from me, but instead, we were so aligned. Just incredible. It made me excited to meet strangers!<br><br>(Part 1)</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-374_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-373_">-  Lauren S.</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-386_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-385_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-384_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-380_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-379_">At the end of 2025, <strong>I'm much more self-regulated than before, have a stronger intuition for what works for me, and feel like I have evolved into a better version of myself, ready for what's to come in 2026.</strong><br><br>If you're thinking about doing this program, I want to say - you have no idea how much you can expand your capacity for the difficult things in life and how much a community of like-minded women AND Monica's leadership can pull you to a new level.<br><br><strong>The level of self-commitment I grew towards my future self was profound this year. </strong>This is the kind of program that honors the feminine side of you by giving you all the tools to structure your life just enough to be able to thrive. If you're on the fence - lean in to it.<br><br>(Part 2)</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-383_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-382_">-  Lauren S.</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-395_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-394_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-393_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-389_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-388_">Before HER Year, I felt very overwhelmed by my to-do list, all the things in my mind, and would kind of just shut down off and on when the overwhelm got to be too much.<br><br>I feel like through HER Year <strong>I was able to learn and, more importantly, implement new strategies and techniques in different areas of my life</strong> that helped make me feel more on top of it, okay with relaxing and taking care of myself, realizing the importance of honoring the season I’m in, and really open my heart to myself and listening to my intuition.<br><br><strong>&nbsp;I also really loved that it was a year-long. It made it actually life-changing instead of something you cram in over two months.</strong><br><br>If you feel stuck, overwhelmed, a little hopeless, but you know you want more, then go for it! It will help you in so many ways, and likely in many ways you can’t even imagine! </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-392_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-391_">-  Karajane D.</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-404_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-403_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-402_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-398_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-397_"><strong>I feel like a completely different woman </strong>after just one year in HER Year. When I look back, I realise just how much has changed.<br><br>In the last year, I landed a dream job, moved to a new city, made incredible new friends, my relationship got better and better, and I’m the most aligned and the happiest I’ve ever been. I truly feel like I’m no longer pushing, and I’m actually enjoying everything I get to experience.<br><br>The work shows. <strong>My partner is always commenting</strong> on how proud he is of me for doing the work, how regulated, happy, and supportive I continue to be.<br><br>The past year has been full of the smallest shifts that continuously allow me to show up as the best version of myself, and this has reflected in every area of my life.<br><br>(Part 1)<br></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-401_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-400_">- Evie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-413_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-412_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-411_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-407_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-406_"><strong>And here's what I want to tell the woman on the fence about joining...</strong><br><br>That life gets to keep getting even better. Whether you’re going through something at the moment, or life is ok and you want it to be f*cking incredible - HER Year gives you the little shifts to do that sustainably. None of it feels like work; it feels like full-on self-care and indulgence that I get to look forward to and tap into all of the time.<br><br>It’s changed my outlook on life, made everything so much easier to execute, and helped me to develop in ways that I didn’t even know I needed to. You’ll get so much more from this programme than you could ever imagine &amp; <strong>if you want to invest in one thing that will uplevel your career, mindset, relationship, and lifestyle - this is the one.</strong><br><br>I am sooo excited for what comes next. I feel like I've had years of working on myself, and after just one year in HER Year, I have a stable foundation where I know that it gets to keep getting better. I’m not sure how to articulate it, but it’s like <strong>for the first time in my life I’m not worried about slipping backwards or trying to fix the next thing or waiting for something to happen </strong>- I know that life gets to be truly magical and I get to shape it and I can’t wait to see what happens of another year in this programme!<br><br>(Part 2)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-410_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-409_">- Evie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-14_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-15_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-16_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-17_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-19_">Three words I'd use to describe my experience inside HER Year: Expansive. Nourishing, Sisterhood.<br><br>I loved the in-person events. It was such a beautiful gift to meet everyone in real life. I am amazed by how people have truly been showing up in the Telegram group the whole year!<br><br>In December of 2024, I was a bit of a wreck. I had lost parts of myself, and I thought I should be further along, given all the work I had done. I was overwhelmed, tired, and living in scarcity (even though I had more than I had ever had before).<br><br>(Part 1)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-20_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-22_">-  Ida</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-23_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-24_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-25_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-26_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-28_">The biggest shifts I've made are: 1) I used to believe that I was not feminine enough when I also loved my work, and 2) Life happens, I'm human, and perfection is not the goal, and I finally feel that in my whole body.<br><br>If you're thinking about joining, know that while you can make everything happen without support, but <strong>if you want it to happen way faster and for the journey to be much more fun, then HER Year is the place to be!<br><br></strong>(Part 2)<strong><br></strong></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-29_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-31_">-  Ida</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-32_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-33_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-34_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-35_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-37_">When I first joined HER Year, it was at a time when I was a first-time mum, and I was confident but not solid in my new identity.<br><br><strong>Now finishing HER Year and hitting huge milestones like having my dream wedding, honeymooning, and moving into a place by the beach (something I've wanted for so long) - I am really proud of myself, and that's huge for me to say.</strong><br><br>Having such a huge year stretched my capacity. But being in HER Year, I embodied so much patience and compassion for myself, a real knowing and belief to make it big instead of dimming myself, permission to have it all and make it happen. I really expanded in so many areas of my life.<br><br>(Part 1)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-38_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-40_">-  Tamra</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-41_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-42_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-43_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-44_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-46_">My relationship was so full of spice and magic, I was so present with Octavia (my daughter), I was very productive with less time, and I really let myself be stretched and honour my emotions through it all. Looking back now, HER Year gave me so many pillars to ground and expand into it all, and I am so grateful.<br><br>My favorite part was the community. <strong>I loved how we were all there for each other; it felt so special and magical going through it all with everyone.</strong> And the guest sessions, I thought they were amazing! The whole experience was expansive, igniting, and grounding.<br><br><strong>If you have big goals, dreams, and you're highly ambitious, you need something to support the human behind it all.</strong> HER Year brought me so much - masculine structure to really streamline my life and give me more time for relationships, being a mum, and running my business without letting life slip. It gave me sisterhood. I felt so seen by the women in this group, we were all moving through so much together, different highs and lows, and we were there - it was really special. This program helped me embody more of my feminine side and sprinkle in pleasure even when life gets busy or chaotic.<br><br>If you want to expand into a new identity, and skyrocket your whole life, or just want support, to feel held through a big and stretching year you know you're going to have, this container holds you through it all. <strong>And most of all, if you're after magic, this is your sign to join.</strong><br><br>(Part 2)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-47_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-49_">-  Tamra</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-50_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-51_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-52_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-53_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-55_">I would describe HER Year in 3 words: Grounding, Supportive, and Accelerating. Or in other words... <em>Everything.I.Needed.</em><br><br>I've been reflecting on what's changed in my life as a result of HER Year, and one MASSIVE thing is that it felt like I stopped chasing to "get something," and I was just living my life and becoming an elevated version of myself!<br><br>After other programs, there was always so much integration that was needed, and here I feel like I am just living. And that<strong> felt like a refresher from constantly needing to heal.</strong> Yes, there will always be things that pop up, but I loved designing my life around intentionality and growth this year vs. what needed healing. I learned through consistency that the results will come. Showing up when it's hard and others might quit, that's when the magic happens. It's not about perfection, it's about being present. And with that, the results DID come.<br><br>(Part 1)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-56_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-58_">-  Stephanie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-59_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-60_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-61_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-62_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-64_">I will bullet some of my tangible wins, so it doesn't feel like you are all reading a novel:<br><br>- <strong>Business $$ growth from $3,700 MRR to $15,900 MRR</strong>, and I am upgrading a contract with an existing client in the next 2 weeks AND starting a new client in January that'll shift upwards!!!<br><br>- I FINALLY got my bloodwork done, found a medical practitioner locally whose values aligned with mine, and while a slow start, I feel held and like I can trust and rest into her wellness plan for me.<br><br>- I hired my first two full time team members and am now in search of my third! Early in the new year, we're also doing a slow ramp up in household support (meal prep/house manager).<br><br>- While my husband and I were in a really painful/destructive year in our relationship, we're building up from a really powerful place as we close the end of the year, and I see the change. It's been a hard year, and now I am seeing all the results compounding; it feels like all at once. He's been helping with the load and splitting it, and it's making everything feel all sparkly and special again.<br><br>- I realized how sacred my energy is and how much I need to protect it, and with that, I said goodbye to 2 friends, 1 client, and 1 client/friend interaction. No huge drama or boundary setting, just pulling back, and turns out once I did, they weren't there anyway.<br><br>- Really, embodied money comes back; time does not. I am usually one who is scared of spending money, and this year, instead of leaning into that fear, I invested my money in things that gave me long-term ROI vs. just having the $$ in my account.<br><br>
(Part 2)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-65_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-67_">-  Stephanie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-68_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-69_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-70_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-71_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-73_">Overall, I feel like I have had the most change in my business this year (if we look at the year as a whole), but my relationship is quickly proving to also be somewhere with massive breakthroughs this year. It's where I needed to spend the most time to unlock what's coming up for me! But I also really moved through some internal blockers I have carried for many, many years.<br><br><em>***There is also a financial win that has been world-changing for me (positive, and I cried), but for some reason, I am scared to share it with anyone except my husband. Once confirmation docs come in in a few days, I will share. I am just still sitting here, shocked about it.<br></em><br>Overall, in terms of how HER Year was delivered, <strong>I love how it's structured to be maximum value, and not super time-intensive.</strong> As someone currently in a phase where there's not enough time to just wash her hair some days, I really appreciated how some months I could spend lots of time sifting and working through the program, and other months where I just did the call and action steps and still took immense value! This was also a surprise, because some months I was shocked that just a call and a couple of action steps were enough, and I felt like I was making real progress. Change doesn't have to be HOURS a day to show progress.<br><br>It's also a Monica container. Which means that, unlike quite a few others out there,<strong> you are not a number</strong>; you are remembered and cared for within the group, no matter your level of engagement.<br><br><strong>I REALLY loved that it spanned over a whole year.</strong> I felt like something was always supporting me and working in my favour without needing to be plugged in all the time. It feels safe and supportive.<br><br>(Part 3)<br></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-74_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-76_">-  Stephanie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-77_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-78_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-79_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-80_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-82_">If you feel the nudge - go for it. I was convinced I wasn’t going to join, and then I signed up at the last minute. I never regretted it - it was worth every penny!<br><br>I have built such a great relationship with myself. My self-trust has increased tenfold. I now know that when I commit to something and say I’m going to do it, I will follow through. I’ve had one of the busiest years of my life, and I’m so proud of how I’ve shown up. I took 95 pages of typed notes on all the content in HER Year - the amount of knowledge I’ve gained over the course of the past year is amazing.<br><br>(Part 1)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-83_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-85_">-  Gabby</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-86_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-87_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-88_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-89_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-91_">My acne has fully cleared, and I had my first period without having to take ibuprofen (literally for the first time since I went off the pill 7 years ago). I feel like things are easy and effortless, and don’t need to be so hard. My relationship with my husband has deepened and is even better (which I didn’t know was possible) - our polarity is incredible.<br><br>I loved the different monthly themes (it made it feel exciting and fun each month), connecting with the other women in the Telegram group, and all the Q&amp;As (might have been my favorite part). I felt like there was so much learning in listening to Monica answer other people’s questions. I also love how I pushed myself to get out of my comfort zone by attending both the in-person events.<br><br>I never felt like a number - I felt like Monica was invested in every single woman’s success throughout the year. I also loved all the behind-the-scenes content around clothes, meals, etc., since it was so tangible. I’m so grateful I did this program, and I can see myself signing up again in the future!<br><br>(Part 2)<br></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-92_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-94_">-  Gabby</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-95_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-96_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-97_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-98_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-100_">I just wanted to say thank you for creating a container that was exactly what I needed this year. Not all personal, not all business, but pretty much everything in between.<br><br>After hiring a business coach for $16,000 last year and them doing NOTHING for me, I was hesitant to invest in this program. However, I knew it was the perfect one as I definitely needed a long-term program (too much on the schedule for short-term programs) and that it covered a variety of topics.<br><br>Some intentions I had for myself were to bring more balance into my life, allow myself to step more into my feminine and help my husband step more into his masculine with me as the breadwinner, and to really establish some habits for me. Oh - and to fall pregnant with ease.<br><br>(Part 1)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-101_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-103_">-  Jordan</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-104_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-105_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-106_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-107_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-109_">Here are a few wins from intentions set - big and small, cause honestly, I’ve learned that they’re all big and compound:<br><br>- travelled almost monthly<br>- matched my previous year's income while working LESS<br>- fell pregnant with ease (1 month of intentional trying) in the month I wanted (May)<br>- pregnant at Christmas with a beautiful bump<br>- relatively easy pregnancy with minimal symptoms and no stretch marks thus far!<br>- established a dry brushing and facial cupping routine (I do one or the other daily and have for 6+ months, even while travelling)<br>- more discipline with workouts and using the black poll to just get them done, because I know how much better I feel<br>- as a double self-employed person (2 income streams) with no maternity leave, saved up $100,000+ to allow us to have at least 6 months of maternity leave without financial worry<br>- was the second-highest-earning dentist in my new practice<br>- created my own personal email list and streamlined systems for our business<br>- more time in the kitchen, with family, and enjoying with friends<br>- started investing aside from savings for maternity leave and payments towards the house we bought<br>- had my husband fully take over our finances and trusted him to do so!<br>- built our dream nursery<br><br>I am sure I have missed some things in that list, but upon thinking about it, I love the variety of what I’ve accomplished and just overall shifted in my life. It’s not all business, not all personal, and not all health-related, but just well-rounded growth.<br><br>Looking forward to the MotHERhood container and really settling into that phase of my life with your help and guidance. It’s been really fun to have a mentor who is 2-3 steps ahead of me in life, goals, marriage, kids, so I know this will be super supportive.<br><br>(Part 2)<br></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-110_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-112_">-  Jordan</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-113_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-114_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-115_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-116_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-118_">You asked me what changed in my life as a result of HER Year, and the simplest answer is: I did, and I did without doing a million things to make it happen.<br><br>I am more grounded, more present, met the man of my dreams, I teach salsa, which I love deeply, I have so much clarity around my job and next steps, I am clear and compassionate and kind with others whilst ensuring my needs are met, my boundaries are solid, and<strong> I am more glowing, more regulated, and I actually feel whole as I am!</strong><br><br>I am different as I am actually living what I wanted and have been able to step towards the things I want without constantly needing to push!<br><br>(Part 1)</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-119_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-121_">-  Rena</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-122_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-123_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-124_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-125_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-127_"><strong>This program was healing, expansive, and supportive in every way.</strong> I loved the community, the richness of the experience, the support, the kindness and care we received constantly, and the realness of being human.<br><br>If you're on the fence about joining HER Year, here's what I want to share with you: <em>GET OFF THE GODDAMN FENCE!</em><br><br>You have the choice, get pushed off the fence by life and have it the "hard" way *OR* make the decision and take your life into your hands, develop this deep self-trust and intuition and see yourself literally flying towards the life that you want for yourself. It really is this easy because <strong>even from simply being in the program, you get an uplevel. </strong>And if you actually do the thing and commit, <strong>you'll get so much more out of your life than you could ever imagine.<br><br></strong>(Part 2)<strong><br></strong> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-128_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-130_">-  Rena</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-131_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-132_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-133_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-134_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-136_">I have never taken on so much in a year, and not once have I felt burnt out, and I KNOW this is from Queen Alchemy and HER Year!!!!! I don't know how to put my transformation into words. I feel like I am operating at a level of me that is far beyond my current reality.<br><br>Time has compressed in HER Year in the best way: I achieved things in the first six months of the year that I expected to take me double or even quadruple the time. I paid off $30K of debt in four months, started my business, met some truly soul aligned women both online and in person through this program, called the version of me I thought I would be in 5 years' time to today, and yet I feel like I have more time on my hands and I'm more present than ever before.<br><br>(Part 1)<br> 

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-137_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-139_">-  Renee</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-140_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-141_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-142_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-143_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-145_">I also started 2025 $30K in debt, and as of October 2025, I am debt-free, have over $30K in savings, and also have an investment portfolio!<br><br>The thing I loved most about HER Year is how the container empowered ME to lead MY life instead of outsourcing guidance to everyone outside of me. The solutions and intuitive steps to creating my dream reality are all within me, and I know how to move from that space now confidently.<br><br>(Part 2)<br></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-146_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-148_">-  Renee</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-149_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-150_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-151_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-152_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-154_">Ahhhh gosh, where do I start?! Wow, okay, let me unpack this...<br><br>Emotionally: I feel more in touch with my intuition than ever before, I trust it more than ever, and feel empowered to do so rather than squashing it down. I felt really lonely at the end of last year, with losing touch with a long-term friend, and I was really craving community and friendship. HER Year has given me that in so many ways, and I’m so grateful.<br><br>(Part 1)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-155_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-157_">-  Laura</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-158_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-159_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-160_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-161_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-163_">Physically: I set myself a weight goal at the end of last year and wrote it down. I now weigh EXACTLY that amount, which is crazy to me!!!<br><br>Relationship: I GOT ENGAGED!! Eek, I wasn’t expecting it this year, but I was open to possibilities, and I must have manifested it!! So happy that I got to share it in the group—so many of the girls wished me congratulations, which filled my heart with love!!<br><br>The monthly calls were also something that kept me going this year, kept me grounded, and was something special to look forward to.<br><br>If you're on the fence about joining, oh girl… JUST GO FOR IT!!! It will enrich you in ways you didn’t expect, and the community will transform your life. This space is truly magical.<br><br>(Part 2)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-164_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-166_">-  Laura</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-167_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-168_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-169_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-170_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-172_">When I joined, I was really looking to immerse myself in the community, uplevel how I show up in my relationship, and improve my commitment to my health. All of these things and more have happened this year, and so much of it is thanks to the continuous value that Monica has provided throughout the entire year - <em>she overdelivered as per usual.</em><br><br>There's also never going to be a container of Monica's in which I don't feel expanded x100 just to absorb all of her wisdom &amp; see what's possible for me (&amp; all of us) when we're living in alignment &amp; have the guts to go after what we want.<br><br>I absolutely improved how I show up &amp; communicate in my relationships - I am so proud of myself for how I handled some difficult situations this year, which would not have gone nearly as smoothly without all of the tools &amp; wisdom I've learned from Monica in HER Year.<br><br><strong>Showing up for my health has also never felt easier</strong> - HER Year has given me the tools &amp; permission slip I needed to understand what optimal health looks like for ME, not what I think I'm "supposed" to do.<br><br>Implementing the masculine structure that Monica teaches has also helped me reduce my stress &amp; feel so much more confident in every area of my life (work, personal life, finances, health, etc.), which has allowed me to naturally relax a lot more without having to sacrifice anything for it. <br><br>(Part 1)<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-173_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-175_">-  Reagan</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-176_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-177_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-178_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-179_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-181_">The masterclasses themselves are gold, and all of the bonus modules &amp; the two calls with Hal were just as expansive &amp; valuable, which really enhanced the experience.<br><br>The in-person events were the most expansive part for me, too. Monica's always been one of my biggest expanders, and being in an intimate space gathered with other women who just GET IT was SO extremely nourishing. There really is nothing like it. And to see <strong>physical proof of what is possible for me &amp; all of us with my own two eyes - the relationship, the health, the wealth, the abundance, and everything else that Monica embodies - literally changed my brain chemistry.</strong><br><br>I'm much more confident standing in my own independence &amp; truth, and no longer feel so easily affected by other people's opinions or worldview - I simply unsubscribe.<strong> Literally just everything has gradually upleveled for me &amp; in ways both big and small.</strong> I am so happy that I joined.<br><br>(Part 2)<br></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-182_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-184_">-  Reagan</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-185_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-186_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-187_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-188_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-190_">If you're thinking about joining, here's what I want to say to you: <strong>There really isn't any way that you won't get your money's worth out of this experience.</strong> There is SO much value across every single piece of content, beyond just the masterclasses, which are already SO good. Monica really doesn't gatekeep anything here. Being able to have my own specific questions answered in the Q&amp;As was SO amazing!!<br><br>You really <strong>can't put a price tag on the expansion you get just from being immersed in a community of like-minded, ambitious, driven women </strong>who are equally as committed to living a life of ease &amp; flow as they are to having a big life &amp; incredible achievements. Part of me feels so healed just from the in-person events, &amp; it was so worth it to take the opportunity to meet other soulfully-aligned women, even if it required getting creative to make these two events work.<br><br><strong>If you're feeling the pull, it's for a reason, and I guarantee you'll get more out of this program than you could imagine. </strong>The wisdom, lessons, community, sisterhood, &amp; everything in between are beyond worth it!!!<br><br>(Part 3)<br></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-191_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-193_">-  Reagan</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-194_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-195_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-196_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-197_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-199_">HER Year has been amazing so far. I feel like we're being fire-hosed with helpful information in the absolute best way. Having an ENTIRE YEAR with Monica to pick her brain, get questions answered, and have time to sit with and integrate the material...it's priceless.<br><br>I'm happy she's increasing the price for next year because it ABSOLUTELY is worth it. Again, I can't say how blown away I am by just how much she's been giving us: the masterclasses, Q&amp;As (multiple per month!), and all the other bonus content.<br> 

<br>It's been incredible connecting with so many powerful ladies! While I certainly don't have relationships/dialogue with all of them, I've begun two strong connections. And one of those two has become a business mentor for me/generating referrals for my own copywriting studio. We didn't go into it trying to become business besties, but we kinda are now! I never would have anticipated that. So, a huge win for me.<br>

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-200_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-202_">-  Niki</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-203_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-204_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-205_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-206_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-208_">HER Year is the one thing I look forward to every single month, every topic is so juicy, and even though I have trained with Monica, done QA and other courses... I am STILL learning and integrating all of the golden nuggets she drops, not only in the live calls every month but in the additional Q and A's that Monica provides after every masterclass.<br><br>There is so much added value in HER Year, it's insane. The community is amazing and full of like-minded women. I'm so excited for the London event, so I can finally meet some of these people in person! I really feel like this year so much has shifted for me already. I feel like I'm truly stepping into the woman I want to be in my life and business.<br> 



</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-209_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-211_">-  Helen</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-212_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-213_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-214_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-215_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-217_">I've just spent the last 2 weeks going through the podcast calls again, and I went back to my goal-setting month, &amp; I know Monica said, 'you might want to reset your goals when you get partway through the year, cos I kinda hope you have changed'.<br><br>And I was looking at my original Pinterest board, and it feels so old me, that's how much has shifted. I can't really describe it, but I already do feel so much more like HER, like the mature woman who CAN do it all. The energetic shift is unreal.

<br><br>(Part 1)<br>

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-218_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-220_">-  Evie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-221_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-222_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-223_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-224_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-226_">Seriously I always knew that I would join again as HER Year has kept me going and elevated me in soooo many ways. I was at dinner last night and could just feel an upleveling and identity shift happening inside of me &amp; it was so so good. I really do feel elevated in ALL areas of life &amp; f*cking love how all encompassing this programme is. The value is actually unreal!!
<br><br>Thank you SOOOO much for this year. I really feel like I have expanded in so many ways &amp; I'm so excited for the next one!

<br><br>(Part 2)<br>

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-227_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-229_">-  Evie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-230_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-231_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-232_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-233_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-235_">The biggest shift I've experienced since joining this program is an increase in my self-respect and self-love. I finally believe that I deserve joy, abundance, and fulfillment. Of course, it’s a daily practice, and sometimes I still fall into old patterns, but I now have the tools, awareness, and structure to come back to balance.<br><br>It honestly surprised me how well-structured this program is and how it’s just perfect for women who want more out of themselves in a graceful and abundant way. 

<br><br>(Part 1)<br>

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-236_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-238_">-  Jessica</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-239_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-240_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-241_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-242_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-244_">Monica, you’ve created such a powerful space. Your energy, authenticity, and mix of strength and softness show us that we really can have it all. And honestly, the fact that you’re a mom, a business woman, have an amazing husband, and still keep yourself so beautiful, ethical, and totally badass like, come on... you’re a true role model and someone I definitely want to keep in my circle.
<br><br>I’m beyond grateful for you, for this program, and for every incredible woman here, and Monica’s amazing team, who make it what it is. 

<br><br>(Part 2)<br>

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-245_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-247_">-  Jessica</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-248_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-249_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-250_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-251_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-253_">I feel like I’ve grown so much, and I can’t wait to see what’s in store for myself! HER Year helped me realize what I really wanted and needed from life. At the beginning of the year, from the NYE Bundle to the HER Year masterclasses on manifestation, it all guided me towards one of the biggest changes in my life in the past decade!<br><br>I quit my job, I’d been working for almost a decade, packed up all my stuff, my husband, and my cat, and moved to Seattle! I’m now a five-minute drive from my family, I’m starting a new job in a new area that will utilize my strengths without all the office drama and politics, and I truly have HER Year to thank. This move was always something I wanted, but was always somehow "two years away."<br><br>HER Year gave me the courage to live the life of my dreams today, and for that, I will be forever grateful.<br> 

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-254_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-256_">-  Mary</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-257_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-258_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-259_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-260_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-262_">I would describe HER Year in 3 words: Grounding, Supportive, and Accelerating. Or in other words... <em>Everything. I.&nbsp;Needed.</em><br><br>I've been reflecting on what's changed in my life as a result of HER Year, and one MASSIVE thing is that it felt like I stopped chasing to "get something," and I was just living my life and becoming an elevated version of myself!<br><br>After other programs, there was always so much integration that was needed, and here I feel like I am just <em>living</em>. And that<strong> felt like a refresher from constantly needing to heal.</strong> Yes, there will always be things that pop up, but I loved designing my life around intentionality and growth this year vs. what needed healing. I learned through consistency that the results will come. Showing up when it's hard and others might quit, that's when the magic happens. It's not about perfection, it's about being present. And with that, the results DID come.<br> 

<br>(Part 1)<br> 

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-263_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-265_">-  Stephanie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-266_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-267_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-268_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-269_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-271_">I will bullet some of my tangible wins, so it doesn't feel like you are all reading a novel:<br><br>- Business $$ growth from $3,700 MRR to $15,900 MRR, and I am upgrading a contract with an existing client in the next 2 weeks AND starting a new client in January that'll shift upwards!!!<br><br>- I FINALLY got my bloodwork done, found a medical practitioner locally whose values aligned with mine, and while a slow start, I feel held and like I can trust and rest into her wellness plan for me.<br><br>- I hired my first two full time team members and am now in search of my third! Early in the new year, we're also doing a slow ramp up in household support (meal prep/house manager).<br><br>- While my husband and I were in a really painful/destructive year in our relationship, we're building up from a really powerful place as we close the end of the year, and I see the change. It's been a hard year, and now I am seeing all the results compounding; it feels like all at once. He's been helping with the load and splitting it, and it's making everything feel all sparkly and special again.<br><br>- I realized how sacred my energy is and how much I need to protect it, and with that, I said goodbye to 2 friends, 1 client, and 1 client/friend interaction. No huge drama or boundary setting, just pulling back, and turns out once I did, they weren't there anyway.<br><br>- Really, embodied money comes back; time does not. I am usually one who is scared of spending money, and this year, instead of leaning into that fear, I invested my money in things that gave me long-term ROI vs. just having the $$ in my account. 

<br> 

<br>(Part 2)<br> 

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-272_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-274_">-  Stephanie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-275_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-276_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-277_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-278_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-280_">Overall,<strong> I feel like I have had the most change in my business this year</strong> (if we look at the year as a whole), but <strong>my relationship is quickly proving to also be somewhere with massive breakthroughs this year.</strong> It's where I needed to spend the most time to unlock what's coming up for me! But I also really moved through some internal blockers I have carried for many, many years.<br><br><em>***There is also a financial win that has been world-changing for me (positive, and I cried), but for some reason, I am scared to share it with anyone except my husband. Once confirmation docs come in in a few days, I will share. I am just still sitting here, shocked about it.</em><br><br>Overall, in terms of how HER Year was delivered, <strong>I love how it's structured to be maximum value, and not super time-intensive.</strong> As someone currently in a phase where there's not enough time to just wash her hair some days, I really appreciated how some months I could spend lots of time sifting and working through the program, and other months where I just did the call and action steps and still took immense value! This was also a surprise, because some months I was shocked that just a call and a couple of action steps were enough, and I felt like I was making real progress.<br><br>Change doesn't have to be HOURS a day to show progress.<br><br>It's also a Monica container. Which means that, unlike quite a few others out there, <strong>you are not a number;</strong> you are remembered and cared for within the group, no matter your level of engagement.<br><br><strong>I REALLY loved that it spanned over a whole year. </strong>I felt like something was always supporting me and working in my favour without needing to be plugged in all the time. It feels safe and supportive. 

<br> 

<br>(Part 3)<br> 

</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-281_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-283_">-  Stephanie</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-284_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-285_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-286_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-287_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-289_">This program was the perfect compliment to Queen Alchemy. After doing that program, I had to redefine my relationship with my feminine energy and self. I felt I leaned way into the feminine energy, which was amazing, but I also picked up some not-so-great habits like not having self-discipline because I "wanted to be free”. HER really allowed me to build masculine structure from a feminine place, and it feels SO different than how my masculine structure was before. Now I’m choosing to do these things for myself instead of forcing myself to do them “because I have to.” It makes all the difference in the world. </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-290_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-292_">- GabriElle</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-293_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-294_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-295_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-296_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-298_">This is unlike any other program Monica has. It’s not healing in the same way; it’s about actually showing up in your life the way your ideal self would (and what that means in a practical way). The live Q+A is worth the cost alone. Monica always shows up with such sincerity and wisdom. It’s invaluable.&nbsp;I also liked having the Telegram channel for reminders throughout the program to keep me coming back to the practices in my day-to-day. Plus, the random audio messages from Monica are fire.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-299_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-301_">- Meghan</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-302_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-303_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-304_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-305_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-307_">Here's what I would say to someone on the fence about joining HER:To be honest, sometimes I wonder how I was holding my life together *before* HER. This program truly changed the way I operate on the day-to-day, not only to reach my life goals but also to feel better every single day. With HER, I have been able to experience a fuller life by really make things happen. I learned that it IS possible to improve how I want to feel at any given moment by making slight changes that make the biggest difference (changing places to work, asking your body how to relax, etc).&nbsp;&nbsp;FYI: My period came back during the program so that was gold!!</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-308_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-310_">- Marianne</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-311_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-312_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-313_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-314_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-316_">Before HER, my mornings were typically stressful. Now, a win for me is that I get to move at a leisurely pace, enjoy my breakfast at the table, drive the actual speed limit to work, and show up early in a calm, joyful mood. It's changed the whole trajectory of my day! Thank you for all the helpful tips, inspiration, and motivation!</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-317_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-319_">- Margot</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-320_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-321_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-322_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-323_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-325_">I joined this program because I knew how I wanted my life to look but I wasn't exactly sure what I needed to do on the DAILY to get myself there. I was looking for ACTIONS to take and man...this program delivers.If you want to overhaul your life in a way that actually feels good and also works for YOU and your daily routine – HER is super easy to digest, fun, and extremely actionable. Since completing HER, my health routine and workday have taken a complete 180. Gone are the days of just suffering with symptoms and not doing anything about it. I feel so much more curious and loving toward my body and I'm excited to be on this new, lifelong journey of loving and taking care of it.&nbsp;</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-326_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-328_">- Makenna</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-329_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-330_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-331_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-332_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-334_">In my third month of HER, I was able to develop my business model and things took off fast from there. I feel like I am telling myself it's okay to slow down because everything is happening fast! I have already been offered an opportunity to bring my expertise to workshops at a very prestigious female club where I live!<br><br>I want to say I would not be here without Monica and the program of HER.<br> <br>It was her third podcast, The Money Fear of Investing in Yourself, that I listened to a year ago that changed my mindset on how I value myself. It launched a stream of inspirational thoughts and showed me the direction I wanted to go in my career. I dove deeper into Monica's work which led me to HER. Once I had the tools in place from this program, I had the space in my life for this business! I am forever grateful. I know deep down that I will be leaning into Monica's expertise SO much more.&nbsp;</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-335_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-337_">- Danielle</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-338_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-339_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-340_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-341_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-343_">ANOTHER WIN: This is the program that keeps on giving! I have seen huge health improvements (better sleep, losing weight, my cycle has come back, and is even more regular than before!) since completing HER - even my mom has noticed!I've also seen success at work. My performance has been recognized by my managers and I have been complimented, and I feel overall more happiness. Thank you again!</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-344_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-346_">- Marianne</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="glide-wrapper"><div style="height:100%" class="sc-iQbOXA sc-fIGKkh llkJEK KHnQY pf-134df04fd9b9-347_" data-pf-type="Slide2"><div class="glide-container"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-134df04fd9b9-348_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-134df04fd9b9-349_"><p class="sc-feopBa gVincu pf-134df04fd9b9-350_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-352_">If you are on the fence about doing the program HER, this is your sign to do it now! I can't express enough how transformative the HER program has been for me. It's unlike any personal growth journey I've ever experienced. The work I did in HER opened a door to a whole new world for me. In just the first two months, I was able to implement changes that led to massive upgrades in my health, self-care, and self-love.<br> <br>I found balance in my responsibilities, and suddenly, everything became more attainable. Friends I’ve known for years have commented on how amazing I look, and my husband constantly tells me that I’m the hottest I’ve ever been. Our relationship has reached new heights—it's healthy, has polarity, and is incredibly spicy. <br>Monica's insights on nervous system expansion have made me a better partner and parent. By the last month of HER, I gained the confidence I needed and I had the room in my life to start my own business, which has taken off faster than I ever imagined. I truly owe this incredible transformation to Monica; it would not have been possible without HER. This program has been an epic life upgrade in countless ways.&nbsp;</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-134df04fd9b9-353_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-134df04fd9b9-355_">- DaniellE</span></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><button type="button" aria-label="Previous" class="glider-prev glider-nav glider-nav-1"></button><button type="button" aria-label="Next" class="glider-next glider-nav glider-nav-1"></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
            </div><div data-section-id="pf-8e4a" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-975_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-976_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-977_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/Her-Year-100_500x.jpg?v=1763752748" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/Her-Year-100.jpg?v=1763752748 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/Her-Year-100_1000x.jpg?v=1763752748 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0641/6613/3991/files/Her-Year-100_500x.jpg?v=1763752748 320w" width="1365" height="2048" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="Her-Year-100.jpg__PID:ee849ff9-2a96-45e7-919a-cd43454bd269" data-pf-type="Image3" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-978_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-979_ pf-heading-1-h3 faq-heading">QUESTIONS</h3><i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-981_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-circle-arrow-down" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-982_"><div class="sc-gOqwAI jjtufm pf-983_ pf-icon-right" data-scroll-to-top="true" data-open-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3"><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-984_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-985_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="feb51a9d-f77b-437f-94b1-4dec9d649f16" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>I'm worried it's not the right time for me...</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-987_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-988_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-989_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-990_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-991_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">I see you trying to make all the excuses as to why this isn't the "right time" or "money is better spent elsewhere right&nbsp;now."&nbsp;So let me lovingly call you out... WHAT DO YOU WANT?<br><br>If you've made it all the way to this point on the page and you're still trying to let your ego call the shots for you...  now is the time to step into your feminine leadership and choose a different story.&nbsp; Claim the life that you want for yourself! Trust your heart because it's *never* wrong. <i>(Seriously, it has a  vibrational frequency five thousand times greater than your brain, so it literally knows the future. If you're being  called towards joining HER, then let that calling be enough of a reason.)</i><br><br>I have women joining me for our live calls at *all* times of the day (including from bed with their cup of tea or  breastfeeding their baby). They make it work, and as a result, they get the results they want.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-993_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-994_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="b14dec9d-649f-46ad-b883-15d49a1d17b8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Do I have to be a mother to join?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-996_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-997_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-998_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-999_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1000_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">No. Whether you’re a mum, pregnant, or want to be a mum someday, this space is for you.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1002_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1003_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="8315d49a-1d17-48f4-9eb0-61c388d2574b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Will you run HER YEAR again? </span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1005_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1006_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1007_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1008_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1009_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">I see you trying to tell yourself "II'll do it next time," and giving yourself all the excuses in the book. Just know that your dreams don't wait. Excuses are just that ... excuses. They're not the TRUTH. Do you want to join us or not? Read the sales page, feel into the program, read the testimonials. <br><br>This is a YEAR-LONG program which allows for your holidays, weddings, and even giving birth - I've given you sooo much spaciousness in this program as to not get overwhelmed or ever feel "behind." It's YOUR unique journey and you get to make it work for you. There's truly no "it's the wrong time" for a year-long program. <br><br>So, yes, I plan to continue running <i>HER Year</i> each year, however, I&nbsp;cannot guarantee the format,&nbsp; intimacy level with me, and price will be the same. <br><br>As all my past clients know, I&nbsp;GIVE MY ALL in my proograms and I will be pouring into this 2026 cohort with so much ENERGY.&nbsp;For what you get included, the price for the value is UNMATCHED, so if you are feeling the butterflies... then I would jump in NOW! Why wait??</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1011_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1012_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="b061c388-d257-4b28-9c42-b743baed12bd" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>When are the live calls?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1014_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1015_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1016_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1017_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1018_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>2026 Call Dates<br></strong><br><b>MONTH 1: </b>Tues, Jan 20 at 3:30pm NYC<br><b>MONTH 2:</b> Tues, Feb 10 at 3:30pm NYC<br><b>MONTH 3: </b>Thurs, Mar 5 at 3:30pm NYC<br><b>MONTH 4 (IN-PERSON): </b>April 25th in Atlanta<br><b>MONTHS 5-12:</b> <i>Call Dates/Times TBD<br></i><br>The Decemer in-person workshop/community event will be Dec 5th in London.<br><br>We'll schedule them out a few months at a time so you can add them to your calendar with plenty of notice! All calls will be recorded and added to a private podcast feed for you to listen, or watch inside the private membership space. <i>Talk about VIBES!!</i><br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1020_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1021_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="42b743ba-ed12-4d45-b390-9da8357cffd9" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>What if I can't make it to the live calls?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1023_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1024_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1025_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1026_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1027_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">All calls will be recorded and added to a private podcast feed for you to listen, or watch inside the private membership space. Talk about VIBES!!</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1029_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1030_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="909da835-7cff-4971-aaea-5e1a3d1f9042" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>How will the program work?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1032_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1033_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1034_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1035_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1036_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>++ On the 1st of each month,&nbsp;you'll&nbsp;receive an email&nbsp;that outlines what to focus on for the&nbsp;month (scroll up to see each month's topic for the whole year).<br></strong><br>The email will include the date/time reminder, Zoom link, and any other pre-recorded bonuses that you can listen to/watch whilst waiting for our live call.<br><br>We will be DRIPPING other pre-recorded videos that relate to the month's topic at the beginning of that month as well so there's never a shortage on juicy content that helps you truly EMBODY <em>HER</em>. But don't worry, busy woman, I'm dripping it and intentionally selecting it monthly&nbsp;to ensure there is no overwhelm and you get what you need. ;)<br><br><br><strong>++ Within 24 hours after&nbsp;each monthly call, everyone will receive a link to the recording. So if you can't make the live call, you will get the recording. <br></strong><br>The replay will be hosted in our private membership space&nbsp;so everything will be in ONE central location.&nbsp;We'll also upload it to an exclusive private podcast so you can listen whilst you cook dinner or drive&nbsp;home from work or whatever—super simple and easy to use.<br><br><br><strong>++ There will be&nbsp;a private Telegram&nbsp;space and that is where you&nbsp;will be able to ask questions, share your wins, and connect with one another&nbsp;in between monthly&nbsp;calls. <br></strong><br>I will drop in&nbsp;mini trainings along the way—like&nbsp;little energy boosts, nuggets, inspiration, or anything that's coming through that I want to share with you guys. <br><br>This will be very behind-the-scenes energy and you get first dibs to the little nuggets that drop in during my most growth-filled, identity-shifting chapter of my life. I’m navigating motherhood, expanding my business, and keeping deep polarity in my marriage—and I want you to walk beside me as I embody what it means to be HER when the circumstances aren’t “perfect.”<br><br>These little audio nuggets will also be uploaded to the private podcast, so you never feel "behind" and feel like you have to scroll back through anything. No FOMO here!!! lol<br><br><em>***PLEASE NOTE: This is a GROUP mastermind-style experience that heavily focuses on the power and expansion of like-minded community! This does not include 1:1 access to Monica.<br></em><br><br><strong>++ There will even&nbsp;be a super next level SEARCH function where you can simply type in a keyword and&nbsp;find what you need to listen&nbsp;to/watch.&nbsp;<br></strong><br>My intention is to make this SIMPLE so you can&nbsp;actually get what you need without breaking a sweat or chipping a nail. ;)<br><br><br><strong>++ Finally, the two in-person days are totally optional so zero pressure to fit that in if it just doesn't work for you and your family. But I really really hope you can come!!!<br></strong><br>There will be one in-person day hosted in my home in Atlanta on April 25th, 2026. The other will be on December 5th, 2026, and we plan to host that at a vibey space in London or Paris.<br><br>Honestly nothing&nbsp;beats in-person and this will rapidly shift what you've already been manifesting inside of<em> HER YEAR.</em> These will be one-day workshop, connection, and expansion days that will seriously level up your <em>HER YEAR</em> experience.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1038_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1039_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="ea5e1a3d-1f90-4235-a6f8-5efb0e587250" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>How long will I have access to the program materials?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1041_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1042_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1043_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1044_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1045_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">You'll have access to the live call replays and pre-recorded bonuses dripped throughout the year-long experience until December 31, 2026.<br><br>All PDFs are yours to download, and therefore have lifetime access to.<br><br>The Telegram space will be open through December 31, 2026, as well.<br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1047_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1048_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="f85efb0e-5872-4003-aa46-5ae87422fa6b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>What if I can't make it to the in-person events in Atlanta and/or London?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1050_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1051_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1052_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1053_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1054_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><em>Firstly, we'd challenge you on whether or not you're future-casting a problem or issue that doesn't exist yet. ;)&nbsp;</em><br><br>So many amazing things happen when you're in these containers and you should EXPECT it to all work out!!&nbsp;AND&nbsp;we also know life is happening for everyone differently, and it's a very real thing that some of you won't be able to make it to one or both of the events.That's totally okay!!&nbsp;<br><br>Of course we'd love to have you, but <strong>HER Year is sooo much more than the in-person</strong>, and those really are just a BONUS for what we'll be unlocking together in 2026. <br><br>So, if you can make one or both or neither of them—HER YEAR is still absolutely worth it for the virtual components as well! <br><br><strong>The in-person is just the sweetest, juiciest cherry on top!</strong> <br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1056_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1057_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="465ae874-22fa-4bce-97e2-e60e52785381" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>This is such a BUSY season for me, and I'm worried I won't be able to juggle it all.</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1059_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1060_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1061_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1062_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1063_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>HER YEAR is literally&nbsp;designed <em>for</em> the busy woman.</strong>&nbsp;<br><br>It's nowhere NEAR the amount of work as my other signature program, Queen Alchemy, if you're familiar with that program. <br><br>It's a monthly masterclass (about an hour), you'll have integration work that's about taking shit <em>OFF</em> your plate not putting it on (read the testimonials!!), all Telegram&nbsp;support and voice messages&nbsp;will be put in the portal/private podcast so you can sift through what you need to listen to. <br><br><strong>I'm VERY&nbsp;purposeful about <u><em>not</em></u> making HER YEAR overwhelming.</strong> <strong>The whole point of <em>HER</em> is to feel like we're doing LESS and yet achieving more.</strong> <br><br>You can join the HER calls whilst breastfeeding or on a walk or cooking dinner. You can tune in and&nbsp;out of the Telegram as needed. You get to make this what you need!! <br><br><strong>This program is about&nbsp;support, community, and expansion—</strong><i>NOT</i>&nbsp;adding more onto your&nbsp;to-do list.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1065_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1066_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="e2e60e52-7853-41df-bb5f-15ecb9949604" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>How is HER YEAR different from Queen Alchemy?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1068_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1069_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1070_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1071_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1072_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Queen Alchemy is the QUEEN of all programs. I take you through my unique healing blueprint so that you can be free of all the stuff blocking you from being the dream version of yourself.<br><br>For QA, think trauma healing, feminine embodiment, sensuality, speaking your truth, confidence, healing your wounds, etc. I guide you through my signature techniques (Monica modalities) to embody your most feminine, sensual, confident, and aligned version of yourself. <br><br>This is a FOUNDATIONAL program that lays the groundwork to create your dream life from.<br><br>Honestly, <i>HER YEAR</i> is different from anything else I've done. It's all about embodiment, taking action, and re-aligning your life. This is very much an action and commitment-focused program. There isn't healing work or trauma release like QA is. It's instead for the woman who wants to&nbsp; put her healing in action&nbsp;to re-align her life in the four areas of influence (health, career, relationships, wealth) so that she can embody "HER." I'll be using 2 main 'Monica modalities' for you&nbsp;over the 12 months to help you expand&nbsp;into this next level.<br><br>If you aren't in a place where you're ready to uplevel (aka you need to work on healing first), then QA may be a better fit. If you're unsure of what's best for you, please share with us a bit about you, what you want to achieve, and what's holding you back in an email to support@monicayateshealth.com and Olivia will be able to guide you (with my help if necessary).<br><br>ALSO, whilst trauma healing is absolutely one of the required pillars to create your dream life, you don't necessarily have to do Queen Alchemy first. Just know when you DO do Queen Alchemy, it'll likely 100x your results combined with&nbsp;<i>HER YEAR.</i><br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1074_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1075_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="5f15ecb9-9496-44ed-8c6a-c5ba28fe62a9" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Do I need to do trauma healing before HER YEAR?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1077_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1078_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1079_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1080_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1081_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Great question! Whilst healing your trauma will support you in finding it easier to embody <em>HER</em>&nbsp;(because you won't have your trauma blocking you), it doesn't mean you can't join <i>HER</i> <i>YEAR<em> </em></i>and get heaps from it!<br> <br>For some people, they prefer to start with more 'action' work like this and then go into trauma healing later because that just excites them more. It's also about what your priorities are.&nbsp;<br><br>Don't be mistaken, you will be healing, growing and expanding MASSIVELY inside of <em>HER Year</em>. Just don't use this program as a substitute for Queen Alchemy because it's nothing like it. The two programs complement each other but are very different and serve different purposes.&nbsp;<br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1083_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1084_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="6ac5ba28-fe62-4981-b4a4-fba361286606" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Is HER YEAR similiar to The Feminine CEO? </span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1086_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1087_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1088_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1089_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1090_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">No. The Feminine CEO is a very comprehensive program about building your business. <i>HER YEAR</i> isn't about building your business. It's about embodying feminine leadership, which is embraced in many facets of life, not just work. <br><br>Lucky for you, I've created the "The Feminine CEO Upgrade" so you can add TFCEO to your HER Year experience, and get the best of both worlds in feminine leadership AND business. <br><br><b><u>CLICK HERE</u></b> to learn more about what's included in that upgrade, and if you're a business owner&nbsp;who knows who knows what a $15K month feels like, is running her business with consistent revenue, and is now ready to scale with strategy, systems, leadership, and support—get yourself into HER Year with the business upgrade ASAP!!<br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1092_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1093_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="a4fba361-2866-46d9-b772-9ad5abc4bebe" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Will there be embodiment practices? Or more workshop-style calls? </span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1095_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1096_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1097_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1098_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1099_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><i>HER YEAR</i>&nbsp;is such a different program than anything I’ve ever done—it's combining EVERYTHING that it takes to really become the dream version of youreslf. So whilst we'll of course have some healing in it, it will be on specific things to help you become the next level version of yourself. <br><br>This is not a trauma healing program—that's Queen Alchemy. This is all embodiment, action-oriented, and creating forward momentum &amp; results in all areas of your life work. <br><br>The embodiment comes through all of the action steps that you will be taking and the rejigging that you will do in your life to really become “HER.” So the embodiment piece is 100% there IN the action steps that we’ll go through and everything that you’re going to integrate.<br><br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1101_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1102_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="729ad5ab-c4be-4eab-a0f6-c86c3243d6fd" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Will there be somatic healing and trauma release?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1104_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1105_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1106_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1107_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1108_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><i>HER YEAR</i> is all about embodiment, taking action, and re-aligning your life. This is a very action and commitment-focused program. There isn't a focus on trauma release but there will be components of healing, of course. If you need to do trauma healing to have the foundation of becoming HER, then please start with Queen Alchemy or do both! We have the next round of QA starting in spring of 2026&nbsp; and you can absolutely do both. <br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1110_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1111_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="f6c86c32-43d6-4d21-bbeb-f6c3fc90169e" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>What if I feel like I don’t have time or I’m already overwhelmed in this season of life?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1113_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1114_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1115_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1116_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1117_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">We can always use the excuse that “I don’t have time,” but the reality is if you feel overwhelmed by life, this is all the more reason for you to join <i>HER YEAR. </i>The more you "don't have time for it", the more you need to do it. This work will help you feel like you have more “control” (in a good way) over your time and less overwhelm. I literally created it FOR the busiest women in my life.<br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-1119_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-1120_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="ebf6c3fc-9016-4e60-b05d-bcc32e380649" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>If I drop questions in the Telegram group are they guaranteed to be answered? </span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-1122_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-1123_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1124_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1125_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-1126_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">While I’ll be actively engaging in the Telegram group and answering as many questions as I can along the way,&nbsp;responses are not guaranteed for every question (that would literally be impossible lol). <i>HER YEAR</i> is designed to foster independence and self-leadership, so this isn’t a space for constant hand-holding. <br><br>For personalized, high-touch guidance I recommend exploring 1:1 coaching options for a more tailored experience if that's what you're looking for!</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-1128_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-1129_"><a href="https://monicayates.myflodesk.com/dez4olktgj" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-emIqIH hFkfQE pf-1130_">OMG I'M IN!!</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></details></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-a22a" data-pf-type="GlobalSection" id="1f5c89fe-783a-49ab-a2ce-9f0f5cedf978" class="pf-1132_" store="[object Object]">
